Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.48,0:20:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,戴比特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.70,0:20:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这里我们来守卫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.86,0:20:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,那你怎么办
